"                                    Buffers:

" From :help window
"       "A buffer is the in-memory text of a file."

" Navigation between buffers:
:buffer 1          " Goes to buffer 1
:buffer Controller " Goes to buffer of file containing 'Controller' in name
                   " Name must be unique within open buffers
:buffers           " List open buffers
:bnext, :bprevious " Navigate through buffers
